rating_comment: Kushal and family were amazing hosts - warm and welcoming. They upgraded me to an AC room in view of the weather and low occupancy, provided a late check-out at a nominal charge, helped with delicious and sumptuous home-cooked meals, and had fun engaging conversations. My stay was comfortable and cozy. The listing is spacious, lush green, home to a lot of pets and everyone (including the staff) is like one big family. Proximity to the airport is a big plus. Thank you Kushal for having me over.
Super cool location, hospitable Kaushal and you get to stay on a farmhouse just by the airport ! value for money ! will stay again
Lovely place. And really great hosts. Made awesome food. The surrounding is awesome and it’s next to the airport.
